The 2018 South African Music Awards went down in Sun City, North West this past weekend. And although the SAMAs are dedicated to honouring the crème de la crème of the country’s musical talents, the red carpet always attracts a lot of attention. This year’s red-carpet did not disappoint at all, with A-list celebrities putting their best foot forward. Take a look at what some of the stars wore to the biggest night in Mzansi music. 